    "class": "gps-552792584305706099 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/smooth-spine/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=552792584171291763&sectionId=552792584305706099)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyWKKy3GSm_text","label":"ggyWKKy3GSm_text","default":"<p>Designed with Spine Health Specialists and Trusted by Leading Nerve Experts Nationwide</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3lLzTDdOS_text","label":"gg3lLzTDdOS_text","default":"<p>Designed with Spine Health Specialists and Trusted by Top Sciatic Pain Experts Nationwide</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBzc-BUFzk_text","label":"ggBzc-BUFzk_text","default":"Eliminate Sciatic Back Pain: One Breakthrough Device Restores Spinal Discs from Home"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWJdOpfCQe_text","label":"ggWJdOpfCQe_text","default":"Avoid Back Surgery: One Breakthrough Device Restores Spinal Discs from Home"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKOQZwDDdJ_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggKOQZwDDdJ_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-dc4757cb-4393-4e49-be23-985d6ed82532.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOeoq5KSo3_text","label":"ggOeoq5KSo3_text","default":"What Is the SmoothSpine Triple Fusion Massager (TFM)?"},{"type":"html","id":"gg541QMMpZW_text","label":"gg541QMMpZW_text","default":"<p>SmoothSpine TFM is a revolutionary at-home device that <strong>helps you eliminate back pain and Sciatica, reduce inflammation and stiffness, and increase mobility</strong> all without needing invasive surgery or relying on pain pills.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggK204xJqMx_text","label":"ggK204xJqMx_text","default":"<p>It is designed to be used for 15-30 minutes per day and it comes with a plug-in cord making it convenient and easy to use, without ever having to wait to recharge the battery.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGw9gxZhIQ_text","label":"ggGw9gxZhIQ_text","default":"How Fast Can I See Results?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTIWMF6Doa_text","label":"ggTIWMF6Doa_text","default":"<p>SmoothSpine will deliver results after the first use, of course, your back will not magically be healed after 1 use however <strong>most users experience a decrease in pain and increase in mobility after just 15-30 minutes.&nbsp;</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghoVeGaVVR_text","label":"gghoVeGaVVR_text","default":"<p>After using SmoothSpine for 14 days, you should experience almost complete relief from daily back pain - you will move easier, walk further, and your whole body should feel decades younger.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEq3zcOzTs_text","label":"ggEq3zcOzTs_text","default":"How Does SmoothSpine Triple Fusion Massager Work?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggN7S5tmqzD_youtubeUrl","label":"ggN7S5tmqzD_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggN7S5tmqzD_vimeoUrl","label":"ggN7S5tmqzD_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggN7S5tmqzD_html5Url","label":"ggN7S5tmqzD_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/1d7401c1caf44072b017951bce82c54a.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQHvkrfTNZ_text","label":"ggQHvkrfTNZ_text","default":"<p>The device features three clinically proven therapies that work together:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_pY699Tzg_text","label":"gg_pY699Tzg_text","default":"<p><strong><u>Dynamic Traction Therapy</u></strong> gently stretches and separates your vertebrae, reducing pressure on pinched nerves and allowing your spinal discs to rehydrate and regain their natural cushioning.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4JFz99Gy3_text","label":"gg4JFz99Gy3_text","default":"<p><strong><u>TargetPoint Massage Therapy</u></strong> has micro-vibration nodes that mimic the hands of a massage therapist, targeting deep knots and tight muscles to release tension, ease stiffness, and promote circulation for faster results.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggp1rRGlpGy_text","label":"ggp1rRGlpGy_text","default":"<p><strong><u>Thermal Circulation Therapy</u></strong> uses heat to boost rehydration and bring healing nutrients to damaged spinal discs.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6YYGqGoMJ_text","label":"gg6YYGqGoMJ_text","default":"<p>Simply lay back for 15 minutes a day and let the Triple Fusion Therapy stimulate the natural healing process in your spine - &nbsp;so you can walk, jump, and sleep again without pain holding you back.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5AnEyK174_text","label":"gg5AnEyK174_text","default":"How Do I Use SmoothSpine TFM?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQC5Rx9hMa_text","label":"ggQC5Rx9hMa_text","default":"<p><strong>SmoothSpine TFM is extremely easy to use. </strong>All you have to do is lay it flat on your bed or floor, position your lower back on top, and press the power button.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbtx4NzI9c_text","label":"ggbtx4NzI9c_text","default":"<p>From here, all you have to do is select the traction, heat, and massage setting that is <strong>most comfortable for you.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglhBQY9Fds_text","label":"gglhBQY9Fds_text","default":"<p>Finally, allow SmoothSpine TFM to turn your stabbing back pain into a feeling of bliss and <strong>relief over the next 15 minutes.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBL5BK-s6P_youtubeUrl","label":"ggBL5BK-s6P_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBL5BK-s6P_vimeoUrl","label":"ggBL5BK-s6P_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBL5BK-s6P_html5Url","label":"ggBL5BK-s6P_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/275d619088e94ed5b4489e52e5f32df3.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPcNXDSciV_text","label":"ggPcNXDSciV_text","default":"Will SmoothSpine TFM Work for Spinal Stenosis And Herniated Discs?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrIon6KC7T_text","label":"ggrIon6KC7T_text","default":"<p>Absolutely. The majority of our customers purchase SmoothSpine TFM because they suffer from spinal stenosis, bulging or herniated discs, or Sciatica and have been told their only option is back surgery.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLSHdiIV3P_text","label":"ggLSHdiIV3P_text","default":"<p>SmoothSpine TFM uses Triple Fusion Therapy to <strong>stimulate the natural healing and rehydration process</strong> in damaged or thinned spinal discs allowing users to live pain-free without the need for going under the knife!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjd3yLzY2V_youtubeUrl","label":"ggjd3yLzY2V_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjd3yLzY2V_vimeoUrl","label":"ggjd3yLzY2V_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjd3yLzY2V_html5Url","label":"ggjd3yLzY2V_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/6dfcc0fe62d74444b86a92877407574b.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggS3GePHfon_text","label":"ggS3GePHfon_text","default":"What If My Pain Is in My Hip or Leg, Not My Back?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFG6AdGk0q_text","label":"ggFG6AdGk0q_text","default":"<p><strong>SmoothSpine TFM is designed to alleviate all Sciatica cases, including pain that radiates into your hip, leg, or foot.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIV0LUdnWf_text","label":"ggIV0LUdnWf_text","default":"<p>That’s because it targets the root cause—<strong>compressed nerves in the lower spine</strong>—rather than just masking the symptoms like other solutions.&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2s3Fu3z9K_text","label":"gg2s3Fu3z9K_text","default":"<p>By gently creating space between your vertebrae, releasing trapped nerves, and improving circulation, <strong>SmoothSpine eliminates the pain at its source, no matter where you feel it.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggkoB4YS-F_youtubeUrl","label":"gggkoB4YS-F_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"gggkoB4YS-F_vimeoUrl","label":"gggkoB4YS-F_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"gggkoB4YS-F_html5Url","label":"gggkoB4YS-F_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/a1f25f5af9b24b289ab66b3be7f76695.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvfxh-DOVf_text","label":"ggvfxh-DOVf_text","default":"How Much Does SmoothSpine Cost?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjaqFOYTBo_text","label":"ggjaqFOYTBo_text","default":"<p>At SmoothSpine, we are committed to <strong>making long-term pain relief affordable and accessible for anyone who needs it.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7gtrWtUJ__text","label":"gg7gtrWtUJ__text","default":"<p>We’ve worked hard to offer this breakthrough technology at a competitive price, without markups, because <strong>we know how expensive other solutions</strong> are such as surgery, weekly physiotherapy sessions, and the constant cost of pain meds.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfEelyLkSE_text","label":"ggfEelyLkSE_text","default":"<p>Our goal is to eliminate all of those costs. Instead, <strong>you just need a one-time payment for SmoothSpine TFM</strong>, which usually retails at $250. However, there is a massive sale until midnight where you can get SmoothSpine TFM for as low as $89 when you select the biggest bundle.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggepQZyukxE_text","label":"ggepQZyukxE_text","default":"Where Can I Purchase SmoothSpine TFM?"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5BgFAsbXG_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg5BgFAsbXG_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-771e134f-1096-4615-81eb-fa441a8c71fb.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggR1WQJD4UZ_text","label":"ggR1WQJD4UZ_text","default":"<p>SmoothSpine TFM can only be purchased online at our <a href=\"https://smoothspine.com/products/tfm-pres\"><span style=\"color:#0056B3;\">official website.</span></a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggb_ZMb46rq_text","label":"ggb_ZMb46rq_text","default":"<p>SmoothSpine TFM is not available in stores, and please do not fall victim to cheap knockoffs - SmoothSpine TFM is a scientifically designed medical device, and just as you would not take unverified pain medication if you did not know what was in it, you should not use a device that you do not know how or where it was designed</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDF1U9uOJJ_text","label":"ggDF1U9uOJJ_text","default":"Is SmoothSpine TFM Safe?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggavy2anxq-_text","label":"ggavy2anxq-_text","default":"<p>SmoothSpine TFM has gone through thousands of clinical trials and is backed by renowned spine health experts - it has been determined that SmoothSpine TFM is 100% safe for daily use.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkAgovtx0b_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggkAgovtx0b_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-0b43845d-941c-4b47-b42c-42fe14112ff1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVEPAomqLy_text","label":"ggVEPAomqLy_text","default":"Can I Use SmoothSpine TFM If I Have a Pacemaker?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDpxrzwgwj_text","label":"ggDpxrzwgwj_text","default":"<p>This completely depends on what pacemaker model you have.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxQncbBP47_text","label":"ggxQncbBP47_text","default":"<p>While SmoothSpine TFM is safe to use with 90% of pacemakers, it’s important that you consult with your doctor before ordering.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsu5ob4kWw_text","label":"ggsu5ob4kWw_text","default":"What If I Am Not Happy With My Purchase?"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5hZqy7Vzl_text","label":"gg5hZqy7Vzl_text","default":"<p>In the unlikely event that you are not satisfied with your purchase, SmoothSpine offers a <strong>90-day money-back guarantee on ALL purchases.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHgs612zsq_text","label":"ggHgs612zsq_text","default":"<p>This means you have 90 days from the time your order arrives at your door to try the product and see how it works for you.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSLY_ACEPl_text","label":"ggSLY_ACEPl_text","default":"<p>If for any reason you are not happy and you have not experienced a complete transformation in your back health, simply reach out to our customer support team at <strong>support@smoohtspine.com</strong>, and they will issue you a <strong>FULL refund—no questions asked.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6V_sIyQGh_text","label":"gg6V_sIyQGh_text","default":"It’s Time to Finally Eliminate Your Back Pain &amp; Sciatica (And Keep It Gone for Good!)"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPVHsBMDSV_text","label":"ggPVHsBMDSV_text","default":"<p>If you're tired of struggling with chronic back pain, Sciatica, and feeling like a burden on your family, then <u>SmoothSpine TFM is exactly what you need.</u></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCR9pMNf_P_text","label":"ggCR9pMNf_P_text","default":"With SmoothSpine TFM, getting started is easy:"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-n9gr3-oK_label","label":"gg-n9gr3-oK_label","default":"<p>Step 1</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqJoxWzxHh_text","label":"ggqJoxWzxHh_text","default":"<p>Click the \"Check Availability\" button below to check if we still have stock (Due to high demand, we sell out fast…).</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeBMVuQeJz_label","label":"ggeBMVuQeJz_label","default":"<p>Step 2</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxUX5yAt3-_text","label":"ggxUX5yAt3-_text","default":"<p>If we have stock, you will land on our secure checkout page, where you can choose the bundle that best suits your needs (The bigger the bundle, the more you save).</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJc2kPVK5Y_label","label":"ggJc2kPVK5Y_label","default":"<p>Step 3</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_ci_s3UbB_text","label":"gg_ci_s3UbB_text","default":"<p>Enter your shipping and billing information on our secure checkout page, and we will begin to pack your order and send it out the very next day.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggiIc82ngmW_label","label":"ggiIc82ngmW_label","default":"<p>Step 4</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3qXa6I1vg_text","label":"gg3qXa6I1vg_text","default":"<p>SmoothSpine TFM will be delivered to your door (ships from our local warehouse within 24 hours on average).</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEUHj4HmHo_text","label":"ggEUHj4HmHo_text","default":"<p>It really is that simple.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggv-34H59h7_text","label":"ggv-34H59h7_text","default":"<p>With our <strong>competitive prices, responsive support team, and commitment to your success</strong>, you can trust SmoothSpine to support you on every step of your back pain journey.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwd-sUAAXx_text","label":"ggwd-sUAAXx_text","default":"<p>So if you're ready to turn back the clock on your spine and get back to living without the constant stabbing pain, <strong>click \"Check Availability\" now and let's begin transforming your life today!</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLCedvH6h6_text","label":"ggLCedvH6h6_text","default":"<p><strong>A Special Offer for Our Readers</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggn-HrkzObE_text","label":"ggn-HrkzObE_text","default":"<p>Claim Your SmoothSpine TFM Now and <strong>SAVE 60%</strong> UNTIL MIDNIGHT</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRqpnTAU1D_text","label":"ggRqpnTAU1D_text","default":"<p>Check availability and take advantage of our discount link by clicking below!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2fynqfSWV_label","label":"gg2fynqfSWV_label","default":"<p>Check Availability Now...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnh0HmgcCI_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggnh0HmgcCI_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-29944fd1-d201-4c74-bc68-3464070030ad.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_fgIh0ti9_text","label":"gg_fgIh0ti9_text","default":"<p>\"<strong>My life took a complete 180 after SmoothSpine!</strong> My doctor recommended it to avoid back surgery, and I wish she'd given it to me years ago. <strong>I even got rid of my back 